rows.label: tlk70000015_05_msg0001
rows.name:
Mauna is suspicious of her, but I think
that we can trust Macmac.

rows.label: tlk70000015_05_msg0002
rows.name:
Ever since she showed up, the
atmosphere in the shopping ward
has changed again for the better.

rows.label: tlk70000015_05_msg0003
rows.name:
It's taken a load off the chairman, too.
We get a good showing at the Chamber
of Commerce meetings, even!

rows.label: tlk70000015_05_msg0004
rows.name:
It's true that better communication has
improved a lot of things, but people are
just more invested now.

rows.label: tlk70000015_05_msg0005
rows.name:
And, to be honest, I think a lot of that
is thanks to Macmac!
